snippet.title: PlayStation - Taisen Renai Simulation - Trifers Mahou Gakuen (2000) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Taisen Renai Simulation: Trifers Mahou Gakuen is a Simulation game, developed and published by ASCII Entertainment, which was released in Japan in 2000.
